{"tid":889733,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Mate 20 Pro 螢幕呈現黃綠怪色   華為：偏色屬正常現象","createTime":"2018-11-04T18:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T16:03:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"eab53699e565ca380c5fd5b2d1e61eb452eedccc","tid":889733,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T18:41:02.000Z","msg":"早前在全球上市的華為 Mate 20 Pro 採用先進的弧形 AMOLED 螢幕，雖然售價非常昂貴，但有顧客就投訴螢幕有問題，表示在螢幕邊緣出現奇怪的黃或綠色。用戶報告指當螢幕背景為深灰或白色時，部份有問題電話的螢幕會在微弱燈光下，邊緣會呈現黃色或綠色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2018-11/03/211808/uniqlo_1_76056103a44fedd314529db8c840c29c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-11%2F03%2F211808%2Funiqlo_1_76056103a44fedd314529db8c840c29c.jpg&h=57bc04ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起初以為是個別事件，影響一兩個用戶，結果反映螢幕有問題的用戶數字卻不斷上升。由於投訴的用戶人數上升，華為亦發出聲明回應，華為表示『Mate 20 Pro 使用市場頂尖的的柔性 OLED 螢幕，其弧形設計提升視覺體驗之餘，亦令持握時間舒服。這設計或會導致在不同角度觀看時，螢幕會出現輕微的變色。當使用環境非常昏暗、螢幕亮度設定太低，或是用深色 Wallpaper 時，變色的情況會被誇大。當偏色影響正常使用的話，用戶可以將電話帶到顧客服務中心尋求協助』。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有用戶表示偏色問題隨著使用時間越長變得明顯，估計是和華為黏合螢幕的膠水有關，不過華為並沒有承認。有外國網站認為華為指 Mate 20 Pro 的螢幕變色為正常現象是在逃避責任，又指現時問題遠比官方的解釋嚴重。今次事故並非所有用戶的電話都受影響，有用戶指出問題的電話螢幕都是由 LG Display 提供，而使用 BOE 的螢幕則沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4Z1Z2K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4Z1Z2K.jpg&h=657dcd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/211808/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4546%2F211808%2F1%2F&d=JoJplUMG5spuYUmwSQcW9AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8b82a019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/211808/1/</a>"},{"pid":"607ab1d34f6efed9939b985c41eff03488f631cd","tid":889733,"uid":81113,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T18:43:04.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227745540e399b51cfbdf3564ecd02e5a087c289","tid":889733,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T18:48:11.000Z","msg":"Cmon mate"},{"pid":"4d9bf93b328cc2860068431d9515ae309694b08a","tid":889733,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"LG MON真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbdcc3a10b7f616e008183a7a915274a0bf7f5d","tid":889733,"uid":15564,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4d9bf93b328cc2860068431d9515ae309694b08a","tid":889733,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"LG MON真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T19:42:25.000Z","msg":"A B mon抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但仲未證實個mon係邊邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159cf76826850d7bd5823ae68b07420354f5505b","tid":889733,"uid":36551,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T19:51:33.000Z","msg":"@邪惡咖啡因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9100b35048e4c0f957bcfc4d5f11c85eda5fc82d","tid":889733,"uid":50267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T20:53:15.000Z","msg":"翡冷翠螢幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189eba841bcc040112aad7c8ff6d0f48110f0732","tid":889733,"uid":182118,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T21:23:38.000Z","msg":"爆炸為正常現象"},{"pid":"24723b38d161ee30f9a4c0dcd2adfc2e89cbd172","tid":889733,"uid":42153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T21:43:23.000Z","msg":"偏色唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a